qFieldDefs:
=$(=(Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Sea)
	,'" [Carrier Name - SEA]"' 
	,'" [Service Provider]"' 	
	,'" [Customer Name]"' 
    ,'" [Container size - SEA]"'
    , '"[Loading Port - SEA]"'
    ,'" [Destination Port - SEA]"'
    ,'" [Country Region - SEA]"'
    , '"[Loading Site - SEA]"'
    , '"[Delivery Term - SEA]"'
    , '"[Item Name]"'
    
    
)))

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Dimension_Sea)
	,'Carriers' 
	,'Service Providers' 	
	,'Customers' 
    ,'Container Size'
    ,'Loading Port'
    ,'Destination Port'
    ,'Country'
    ,'Loading Site'
    ,'Delivery Terms'
    ,'Item Name'

       
)

& ' By ' 

&

Pick (

$(v_Switch_Measure_1)
,'Waybills'
,'Containers'
,'Purchase Orders'
,'Shipment Net Weight'
,'Unit Price (Purchasing)'
,'Unit Price (Selling)'

)

byMeasureDef.label: Measure
byMeasureDef.key:
Pick (

$(v_Switch_Measure_1)
,count({<  [Freight Type] = {'SEA'}  >} distinct  [Waybill Number])
,count({<  [Freight Type] = {'SEA'}  >} distinct  [Container Number])
,count({<  [Freight Type] = {'SEA'}  >} distinct  [Purchase Order Key])

)
